### =========================================================================
###  [ 5 ] BATCHES ENDPOINT (/batches) - PROTEGIDO (REQUIERE TOKEN)
### =========================================================================

### 5.1 Procesar Batch (processBatch)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: text/xml; charset=utf-8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:enf="http://soap.model.server.enfok/">
   <soapenv:Header/>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <enf:processBatch>
         <!-- Parámetro request de tipo BatchRequestDto -->
         <request>
            <batchId>Batch-X-101</batchId>
            <data>Datos a procesar para testear</data>
         </request>
      </enf:processBatch>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

### 5.2 Error de Batch Vacío
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: text/xml; charset=utf-8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:enf="http://soap.model.server.enfok/">
   <soapenv:Header/>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <enf:processBatch>
         <request>
            <batchId></batchId>
            <data>A fallar 123</data>
         </request>
      </enf:processBatch>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
